  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">A triangle has a base length of <math alttext=\"56\"><mn>56</mn>\n</math> centimeters and a height of <math alttext=\"112\"><mn>112</mn>\n</math> centimeters. What is the area, in square centimeters, of the triangle?</p>",
